  • Terminally Deprecated Elements
    Element
    Description
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.Comparators.comparableComparator()
    Use Comparator.naturalOrder() instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.HexUtils.convertToHexString(byte[])
    Use HexFormat.formatHex(byte[]) instead, like this: 
    String s = HexFormat.of().withUpperCase().formatHex( bytes );
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.internal.TSIDImpl
    Do not use any longer! This is not tested!
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.SecurityUtils.SHAHASH_Length
    Use SecurityUtils.SHA1HASH_Length instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.checkText(String, CharSequence, int)
    Replaced by StringUtils.checkTextLen(String, CharSequence, int)
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.checkTextNull(String, CharSequence, int)
    Replaced by StringUtils.checkTextLenNull(String, CharSequence, int).
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.escapeUnicode(char)
    Use CharSetUtils.escapeCharacter(char) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.escapeUnicode(int)
    Use CharSetUtils.escapeCharacter(int) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.findVariables(CharSequence)
    Use Template.findVariables(CharSequence) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.format(String, Object...)
    SharedFormatter got obsolete. See there.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.format(Locale, String, Object...)
    SharedFormatter got obsolete. See there.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.FORMAT_INITIAL_BUFFERSIZE
    No longer used!
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.hasVariable(CharSequence)
    Use Template.hasVariables(CharSequence) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.isValidVariableName(CharSequence)
    Use Template.isValidVariableName(CharSequence) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.isVariable(CharSequence)
    Use Template.isVariable(CharSequence) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.joinString(CharSequence[], char)
    This method is obsolete; the same effect can be achieved easily by calling String.join(CharSequence, CharSequence...).
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.joinString(CharSequence[], CharSequence)
    Use String.join(CharSequence, CharSequence...) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.joinString(Iterable<? extends CharSequence>, char)
    This method is obsolete; the same effect can be achieved easily by calling String.join(CharSequence, Iterable)
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.joinString(Collection<? extends CharSequence>, CharSequence)
    Use String.join(CharSequence,Iterable) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.joinString(Stream<? extends CharSequence>, CharSequence)
    This method is obsolete; the same effect can be achieved easily by calling Stream.collect(java.util.stream.Collector) on the stream, with the collector joining() as its argument.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.maxContentLength(Iterable<? extends CharSequence>)
    Use StringUtils.maxContentLength(CharSequence[]), StringUtils.maxContentLength(Collection), or StringUtils.maxContentLength(Stream) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.replaceVariable(CharSequence, Function<? super String, Optional<String>>)
    Use Template.replaceVariable(CharSequence, Function) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.replaceVariable(CharSequence, Map<String, ? extends Object>...)
    Use Template.replaceVariable(CharSequence, Map[]) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.toUnicode(CharSequence)
    Use instead CharSetUtils.convertUnicodeToASCII(java.text.Normalizer.Form, CharSequence) with Normalizer.Form.NFKC as the first argument.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.unescapeUnicode(CharSequence)
    Use CharSetUtils.unescapeUnicode(CharSequence) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.unicodeEscape(char)
    Use CharSetUtils.escapeCharacter(char) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.unicodeEscape(int)
    Use StringUtils.escapeUnicode(int) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.VARIABLE_PATTERN
    Use Template.VARIABLE_PATTERN instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.StringUtils.VARIABLE_TEMPLATE
    Use Template.VARIABLE_TEMPLATE instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.SystemUtils.determineOutsideIPAddresses()
    Use SystemUtils.determineOutboundIPAddresses() instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.SystemUtils.getPseudoNodeId()
    Use SystemUtils.createPseudoNodeId() instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.SystemUtils.replaceSystemVariable(CharSequence, Map<String, ? extends Object>...)
    Use Template.replaceVariableFromSystemData(CharSequence, Map[]) instead.
    org.tquadrat.foundation.util.TSID
    Do not use any longer! This is not tested!
